{"tid":1804946,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉兆佳：警察執法手段愈趨見效  料明年港暴力示威減少","createTime":"2019-12-31T10:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T11:12:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0abfeb4f5d0e7b5d5aa8c4cb65986f361725a1","tid":1804946,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://assets.wenweipo.com/image/2019/12/31/liangmeiling_5f619a224b6a7f5a96fc17aa84b06361.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wenweipo.com%2Fimage%2F2019%2F12%2F31%2Fliangmeiling_5f619a224b6a7f5a96fc17aa84b06361.jpg&h=b3db3254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳昨日接受香港中通社訪問時表示，因警察執法手段愈趨見效，反對派「兵源」受到重大打擊，加上經濟嚴重受損，令市民厭惡暴力行為，預計明年香港暴力規模和力度將逐漸減少。劉兆佳說，經過長期暴亂後，愈來愈多人會逐漸認識到這場暴力背後的本質，並意識到繼續鬥爭下去只會令香港承受更大損失。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳表示，這場社會動亂的本質是以美國為首的外部勢力與本地反華勢力聯手，藉修例風波以達到更大的政治圖謀。他指出，雖無法預計民意在1年之內會否有重大轉變，但他堅信民眾逐漸能看清暴力本質，以及香港的核心利益在哪，對反對派越來越不利，也離他們所希望達到的目標越來越遠。"},{"pid":"bce3fe2f72327775d020bb6c9d199217d5a35a83","tid":1804946,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"<code>德美 聯署 整合</code><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"},{"pid":"19c43e2bd6edac2958437bfda39b286470db9b2b","tid":1804946,"uid":25424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"即係有排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676fbf2dbcb2ed85fa76c7911f354de2d08ed276","tid":1804946,"uid":181789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:42:58.000Z","msg":"做咩姐佢.... 日日出黎吠"},{"pid":"fd1609fad6f7fa488180e2bb5138a73f366f9238","tid":1804946,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2556bfa9f390c13f6a32aa7139af81ff0d6e9df2","tid":1804946,"